  <refentry xml:id="function.str-shuffle" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
   <refnamediv>
    <refname>str_shuffle</refname>
    <refpurpose>Mischia una stringa in modo casuale</refpurpose>
   </refnamediv>
   <refsect1>
    <title>Descrizione</title>
     <methodsynopsis>
      <type>string</type><methodname>str_shuffle</methodname>
      <methodparam><type>string</type><parameter>str</parameter></methodparam>
     </methodsynopsis>
    <simpara>
     <function>str_shuffle</function> mischia una stringa.  Viene generata
     una di tute le possibili permutazioni.
    </simpara>
    <para>
     <example>
      <title>Esempio di uso di <function>str_shuffle</function></title>
      <programlisting role="php">
<![CDATA[
<?php
$str = 'abcdef';
$shuffled = str_shuffle($str);

// This will echo something like: bfdaec
echo $shuffled;
?>
]]>
      </programlisting>
     </example>
    </para>
    <simpara>
     Vedere anche: <function>shuffle</function> e <function>rand</function>.
    </simpara>
   </refsect1>
  </refentry>

